bodyEn:
1. I accidentally sent Rs. {AMOUNT} from VPA {VPA} to VPA {VPA_PAYEE} on {TXN_DATE} (UTR {UTR}). I have contacted the recipient and they refuse to refund. Per RBI's NPCI DRM process, the receiving bank must act on a beneficiary-bank request within 2 working days. Please file the DRM.

Attachments: UPI transaction screenshot, PSP complaint acknowledgement, bank statement extract for the debit.

Regards,
{USER_NAME}
Mobile: {MOBILE_NO}

bodyHi:
